com.xrtb.pojo

Class BidResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xrtb.pojo.BidResponse

  • public class BidResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that handles RTB2 bid response. The BidResponse is built up using a String buffer. At the close of the construction, macro substitutions are applied and then it is converted to a string to be used in the HTTP response.
    Author:
    Ben M. Faul
